snippet.title: Shogun Showdown - Launch Trailer | PS5 & PS4 Games
snippet.description:
https://store.playstation.com/concept/10010714

Shogun Showdown lands on PlayStation! A turn-based combat game with roguelike and deck-building elements, position yourself and attack at the right time, upgrade your tiles and combine them to prepare to take on the Shogun!
